              <h2>How this hash generator works</h2>
              <p>
                This tool computes hashes entirely in your browser using the Web
                Crypto API (for SHA-family algorithms) and well-known JavaScript
                implementations for MD5, SHA-3 and RIPEMD-160. Your input text,
                files, salts and keys never leave your device.
              </p>
              <p>You can:</p>
              <ul>
